text: Vaudeloges is a former commune. It is in the Normandy region in the Calvados department. This is in the northwest of France. On 1 January 2017, it was merged into the new commune of Saint-Pierre-en-Auge.Arrêté préfectoral 19 December 2016 == References == Category:Former communes in Calvados
title: Vaudeloges
